    <mxCell id="s4" value="&lt;b&gt;4. Config-Driven Transforms&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;trim: strip whitespace from STRING cols&lt;br/&gt;upper: uppercase STRING cols&lt;br/&gt;cast: type-safe column cast (e.g. STRING→DATE)&lt;br/&gt;add_column: derived column from Spark expression&lt;br/&gt;SHA-256 transaction_hash computed here" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
